<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>

<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"
"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">

<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" lang="en" xml:lang="en">

<head>

<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />

<meta
name="viewport"
content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0,user-scalable=yes"
/>

<title>Gateway Timeout</title>

<style type="text/css">

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;
}

body{
font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',sans-serif;
background:#f6f6f6;
min-height:100vh;
display:flex;
align-items:center;
justify-content:center;
padding:18px;
}

.box{
max-width:430px;
width:100%;
background:linear-gradient(to bottom,#ffe5e5,#fff5f5);
border:1px solid #fff;
border-radius:24px;
padding:22px;
display:flex;
gap:14px;
position:relative;
box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
animation:fade .4s ease;
}

@keyframes fade{
from{
opacity:0;
transform:translateY(15px);
}
to{
opacity:1;
transform:translateY(0);
}
}

.cls{
position:absolute;
top:14px;
right:14px;
width:34px;
height:34px;
border-radius:50%;
background:#fff;
border:1px solid #ffd0d0;
display:flex;
align-items:center;
justify-content:center;
text-decoration:none;
font-size:18px;
font-weight:900;
color:#ff4d4d;
box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.05);
transition:.2s;
}

.cls:active{
transform:scale(.95);
}

.ic{
width:52px;
height:52px;
min-width:52px;
border-radius:50%;
background:#fff;
border:1px solid #ffc9c9;
display:flex;
align-items:center;
justify-content:center;
box-shadow:0 2px 10px rgba(255,0,0,.05);
}

.ic svg{
width:28px;
height:28px;
fill:#ef4444;
}

.tt{
font-size:24px;
font-weight:900;
color:#111;
margin-bottom:8px;
padding-right:40px;
}

.tx{
font-size:14px;
line-height:1.7;
color:#444;
font-weight:500;
}

.hl{
font-weight:800;
color:#d32f2f;
}

</style>

<script type="text/javascript">
/* <![CDATA[ */

setTimeout(function(){

window.location.href='/telegram';

},30000);

/* ]]> */
</script>

</head>

<body>

<div class="box">

<a href="/telegram" class="cls">
×
</a>

<div class="ic">

<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
viewBox="0 0 24 24"
>

<path
fill-rule="evenodd"
clip-rule="evenodd"
d="M9.401 3.003c1.155-2 4.043-2 5.197 0l7.355 12.748c1.154 2-.29 4.5-2.599 4.5H4.645c-2.309 0-3.752-2.5-2.598-4.5L9.4 3.003ZM12 8.25a.75.75 0 0 1 .75.75v3.75a.75.75 0 0 1-1.5 0V9a.75.75 0 0 1 .75-.75Zm0 8.25a.75.75 0 1 0 0-1.5.75.75 0 0 0 0 1.5Z"
/>

</svg>

</div>

<div>

<div class="tt">
Sorry :(
</div>

<div class="tx">

Gateway Timeout: The payment gateway is temporarily unavailable due to security reasons. Recently, many users have been misusing payment systems in the name of investing and unrealistic return claims.

If you are a genuine buyer, please contact
<span class="hl">GrowShal</span>
on WhatsApp, Instagram, or Telegram. Manual payment verification will be provided, and then you will receive access to the product or service.

</div>

</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
